<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>e.g. I want to have the Zend_Dojo_Form_Element_NumberTextBox allow any numbers with 0 to 6 places.
in dojo you have to set the places constraint to: 0,6
That isnt possible with the Zend_Dojo_Form_Element_NumberTextBox - setPlaces Function, because it converts the given var to integer:
line 135: $this-&gt;setConstraint('places', (int) $places);</p>

<p>the (int) should be removed</p>

