        <div class="body">
            <p>A range for places can be set using constraints, like:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$this-&gt;addElement(
    'NumberTextBox',
    'number',
    array(
        'label' =&gt; 'Number',
        'constraints' =&gt; array(
            'places' =&gt; '0,6'
        )
    )
);
</code></pre>

<p>I'd leave the setPlaces as is and close this as a won't fix. Thoughts?</p>

